{"type":"message","id":"552773c3","parentId":"552a1ee9","timestamp":"2026-03-23T07:15:02.965Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:66549787-5cce-4339-9ae7-e078032c9ded 思考共产主义] 请思考一下共产主义如何实现，从理论、实践、经济、社会等多个角度进行分析，并总结一个简短的观点。不需要太长，但要有深度和思考。\nCurrent time: Monday, March 23rd, 2026 — 15:15 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-23 07:15 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774250102958}}
